additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: YEAST EXTRACT AND CREAM CHEESE BLEND. INGREDIENTS: GLUTEN FREE VEGEMITE YEAST EXTRACT (30%) (YEAST EXTRACT, NATURAL COLOUR (150a), SALT, MINERAL SALT (508), FLAVOURS, NIACIN, THIAMINE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLATE), WATER, CREAM CHEESE (17%) (MILK, CREAM (MILK), SALT, VEGETABLE GUM (410), STARTER CULTURE), BUTTER (CREAM (MILK), WATER, SALT), NATURAL COLOUR (150a), CHEESE (4%) (MILK, SALT, STARTER CULTURE, ENZYMES), HUMECTANT (422), MINERAL SALT (339), THICKENER (1442), FOOD ACID (270), PRESERVATIVES (200,234).

description: Tastes like Australia with cheese! A tasty blend of two Aussie classics, VEGEMITE & Cheese made with Bega Cream Cheese. Scoop it. Snack it. Spread it.
name: Cheesybite Spread
